# Tauri dev watcher exclusions.
# In dev mode the frontend loads from Vite dev server (devUrl in
# tauri.conf.json), not from src-ui/dist. Watching dist causes spurious
# "file changed → rebuild application" triggers on startup whenever
# leftover build artifacts from `npm run build` exist, leading to a
# needless double-compile before the app even opens.
src-ui/dist/
src-ui/node_modules/

# Never needs watching — build/artifact dirs.
target/
Web-Home/
docs/
